    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Main halls of temple complexes which usually housed the primary statues of buddhas or bodhisattvas. For the main halls of some early Buddhist temples (into the 8th century), use kondō.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
